title: Jewish Adherents Congregations and Adherent Rates, US by County, 2007
name: Jewish Adherents Congregations and Adherent Rates, US by County, 2007
description: This data set was found online at the Association of Religious Data Archives (ARDA) website. http://www.thearda.com/ . This data set shows information on religious groups throughout the United States. All data was uploaded as a polygon shape file by county in the United States. This Data set shows the Total congregations, Total Adherents, and Rate of Adherence per 1000 population for the Jewish religion.

author.source: The Association of Religious Data Archives
